<https://w3id.org/mqto#Countermeasure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A remediation procedure that mitigates one or more Failure Modes. Countermeasures are structured as ordered sequences of CountermeasureSteps, represented via the mqto:List pattern for reusability. As a subclass of pko:Procedure, countermeasures align with the Procedural Knowledge Ontology's procedure modeling patterns while maintaining integration with the LIS specified/actual architecture."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Countermeasure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Countermeasure"@en .
