<https://w3id.org/mqto#Material> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Raw materials, consumables, and inputs to manufacturing (the 'M' in Ishikawa's Material). Represents specified material types that participate in Methods. Domain-specific ontologies can define specific material types such as alloys, lubricants, and consumables. Materials can have properties monitored via Signals and associated quality Metrics."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Material> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Material"@en .
