<https://w3id.org/mqto#Method> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A manufacturing process or procedure (the 'M' in Ishikawa's Method). Represents the specified activities and steps in manufacturing. This includes operations and procedures specific to the manufacturing domain. Methods can be decomposed into sub-methods and have Machines and Materials as participants."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Method> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Method"@en .
