<https://w3id.org/mqto#Metric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A specified calculation or key performance indicator (KPI) that bridges quantitative sensor data and qualitative failure detection. Reads from one or more Signals, applies an assessment method over a time window, and compares results against threshold bounds to detect anomalies. Belongs to an IshikawaItem and is referred to by Failure Modes. The actual-layer counterpart is MetricAssessment."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Metric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Metric"@en .
