<https://w3id.org/mqto#MetricAssessment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An instance-layer evaluation that implements a Metric specification by computing a value from actual Observations and comparing it against threshold bounds. Calculated for an ActualIshikawaItem at a specific time, based on observations within a time window. Produces both a calculatedValue (quantitative result) and assessmentValue (boolean pass/fail). When threshold violations are detected, raises FailureOccurrences."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#MetricAssessment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Metric Assessment"@en .
