# https://w3id.org/mqto#Result
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Result> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Result> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Result> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Result> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The outcome of an Observation, containing the measured value (via measValue or other result properties). Subclass of sosa:Result. MetricAssessments extract result values from these Result instances using the resultProperty meta-property to specify which data property should be read."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#Result> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Result"@en .
